column2: SELECT    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,     (p.u-p.r) as &&&, (p.r-p.i) as &&&, (p.r-p.z) as &&&, (p.g-p.r) as &&&,   p.type as obj_ph_type,p.petroRad_u,p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z,   p.petroRadErr_u,p.petroRadErr_g, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroRadErr_i, p.petroRadErr_z,   s.specobjid, s.class as obj_sp_type, s.subclass as obj_sp_subtype, s.z as redshift,    #*(POWER(#, #)*POWER(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT), #))*(em.Flux_Hb_# * POWER(#, #)) as lumin into mydb.dr1#_lcg      from PhotoObj AS p, SpecObj AS s, emissionLinesPort as em      WHERE    s.bestobjid = p.objid   AND p.objid = em.specObjID   AND em.EW_Hb_# > #   AND #*(POWER(#, #)*POWER(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT, DEFAULT), #))*(em.Flux_Hb_# * POWER(#, #)) > (#*(#^#))
